# grok-install — .gitattributes
# Mark generated/landing-page assets as vendored so GitHub language stats
# reflect the actual spec + tooling source (YAML + JSON + Markdown).

*.html linguist-vendored
*.css  linguist-vendored

# Enforce LF line endings across the repo for portability.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Treat binary asset types as binary (no diff, no text conversion).
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.mp4 binary
*.mov binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
